node.text: Welcome to Manchester @cristiano !! Who is looking forward to ronaldo playing again in the premier league?

@JacobandCo Astronomia Art Dragon White Gold Baguette is an original work of art guided by exceptional craftsmanship. The centerpiece of this watch is a 24K rose gold dragon spread throughout the watch case intertwined within the iconic Astronomia complications, which include the double axis tourbillon, the exclusive “Jacob Cut” spherical diamond with 288 facets and the magnesium blue lacquered globe. The latter two artistic elements perform a complete rotation every 60 seconds.

node.text:
@JacobandCo Astronomia Art Dragon Mother Of Pearl 😍

What sets this watch apart from others is its sense of occasion, created by the stunning sapphire Crystal and precious metal case.

Within the Sapphire, Crystal dome lurks the mystical dragon handcrafted by the artisans at Jacob & Co from 18k gold. One other feature unique to this iteration of the ‘dragon’ series is the base dial made entirely of mother-of-Pearl.

Thanks again to @jacobandco for allowing us to showcase this watch with breathtaking designs.

node.text:
3D Screens in China are next level 😳
Via @sir
📷 @khanjipeerwala

@jacobandco Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon encrusted in diamonds is just piece of ART. The case is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron and the movement, or “engine block,” intended to duplicate the Bugatti engine, is placed under a massive sapphire crystal, on display for all to see. With the push of right-hand crown of the timepiece the engine comes to life, just like a true internal combustion engine. The movement is comprised of 578 components). @jacobandco has done something no one has ever even attempted before – to seamlessly combine engines and watches.
